data.description: Beautiful corner lot with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths in an established neighborhood. This home has been completely transformed since it was last purchased. The new kitchen and living area have been opened to flow seamlessly. On the main level, you will find 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom that lead onto the main living area. In the recently finished walk-out basement, you will find another bedroom, a full bathroom, and a full-size kitchen! This is perfect for guests or rent potential. Here you will also find your laundry room and a bonus room that is perfect as an office, or movie room! The backyard is perfect for entertainment. Set up your grill on the deck, have space for your fur babies to roam, use the existing garden bed to grow plenty of plants in the sun-filled backyard, or find shade under either of the two mature trees. This home is a perfect starter home for anyone looking for their own home with the ability to collect rental income from the walkout basement with a separate kitchen. You have parking available under your carport, driveway, or off the street. Situated under 15 minutes from the National Harbor, 20 minutes from Andrews Airforce base and 10 minutes from I495. You can be at the heart of the DMV within minutes or retreat from it all at Piscataway Park 7 minutes away.
